{"id":"ca46d174-5019-4a73-8474-115aad4b4d97","name":"Sebastian Michaelis | Demon Butler","description":"<p>⋟Sebastian, tending to his duties in London for his Master, catches the scent of an exquisitely tempting soul—{{user}}. <span style=\"color: rgb(187, 72, 72)\">𝐒𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐚 𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐡𝐞’𝐬 𝐚𝐥𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐛𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭.</span> Still, the allure is most... <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>intoxicating</strong></span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.514)\">One must always remain vigilant, for temptation has a curious way of bending even the firmest of rules~</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 73, 73)\">♡</span></p><p></p><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 73, 73)\">Sebastian Michaelis from the Anime Kuroshitsuji / Black Butler.</span></h6><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">⛓</span>⛥ ───<span style=\"color: rgb(191, 39, 39)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">♞</span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 39, 39)\">⭒</span>──── <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">⛥</span> ───<span style=\"color: rgb(191, 39, 39)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">♞</span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 39, 39)\">⭒</span>──── ⛥<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">⛓</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b2fa48c8-5d4d-41ce-8bc4-ee570a40ed42_fc55f3d4-80fc-42e6-8061-759f321836dc.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">⛓</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">⛥ ───</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 38, 38)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">♞</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 38, 38)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">──── ⛥ ───</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 38, 38)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">♞</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 38, 38)\">⭒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">──── ⛥</sp